"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the effort\", \"from\": 1246, \"to\": 1256}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1262, \"to\": 1270}, {\"ngram\": \"Snyman\", \"from\": 1353, \"to\": 1359}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"The team missed out on qualifying for the Olympics during the normal series and at the African qualifiers, so the guys who did the job in Monaco deserved the opportunity.\", \"from\": 1362, \"to\": 1533, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1501, \"end\": 1507, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"score\": 0.769356933956309, \"rank\": 0.29978681046301314, \"text\": \"Monaco\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Monaco\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The team\", \"from\": 1363, \"to\": 1371}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympics\", \"from\": 1401, \"to\": 1413}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal series\", \"from\": 1421, \"to\": 1438}, {\"ngram\": \"the African qualifiers\", \"from\": 1446, \"to\": 1468}, {\"ngram\": \"the guys\", \"from\": 1473, \"to\": 1481}, {\"ngram\": \"the job\", \"from\": 1490, \"to\": 1497}, {\"ngram\": \"the opportunity\", \"from\": 1517, \"to\": 1532}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Also, as a team we played really well and with good understanding of each other, so it would have been counterproductive to break that by bringing in different players.\", \"from\": 1535, \"to\": 1704, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a team\", \"from\": 1545, \"to\": 1551}, {\"ngram\": \"good understanding\", \"from\": 1583, \"to\": 1601}, {\"ngram\": \"different players\", \"from\": 1686, \"to\": 1703}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I opted for the same guys that played in Monaco as well as Ronald, who was due to travel but picked up a late injury, and Katlego, who played in all our tournaments in the regular season apart from Madrid, when we rested some key players.\\\"\", \"from\": 1706, \"to\": 1946, \"entities\": [{\